Class InstinctModeModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.instinct.InstinctBaseModule
      • ccre.instinct.InstinctModeModule

  • public abstract class InstinctModeModule
extends InstinctBaseModule
    An Instinct module that can be added to an InstinctMultiModule. This is relevant if you want multiple autonomous modes to easily switch between.
